				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Just in case nobody else has posted it yet.  The flag in the nro camp can and will grab ahold of you if you imediatly backup after porting there using a magus.  
<br />

<br />
After its got ahold of ya you cannot cast or jump to get out,  you can sit down and camp out but when you get back your still there.
